Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:13.62,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Musel jsem ji poslouchat už tisíckrát...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:24.09,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K35}da{\K25}re {\K59}ni {\K39}mo {\K78}{\K28}ki{\K28}zu{\K29}ka{\K28}{\K28}re{\K36}na{\K21}i {\K36}{\K21}i{\K32}ki {\K29}ga {\K31}{\K26}to{\K33}ma{\K23}ru {\K32}yo{\K27}u {\K29}na {\K27}ko{\K37}i {\K29}no {\K23}ko{\K29}ko{\K19}ro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:24.09,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Mé srdce lapá po dechu, zatímco si nevšímáš mé lásky.
